{"id": "1405624123077427270", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "After theory crafting for a while, this is my answer to kath comp.\nGiving clem wheel to karen might be better cuz she needs the aliemus for overexalt.\nHow team works:\n- Tawil pull horla fear card from exalt\n- Tawil pull every sustain option from exalt as she's solo tanking\n- clem and tawil build str\n- kath build combust\n- karen oe then collect all 3 mawate\nOnce you have clem 15 debuff stacks + 3 mawate cards + some wing 4 + at least 10 combust, you're ready to burst for over 1m damage. \nStep 0.5: tawil apply vulnerability... If she can \nStep 1: clem debuff\nStep 2: tawil wing 4 as much as she can\nStep 3: mawate mawate 9 times for 9 arithmetica and apply vulnerability... Just trust, if you mawate along karen will do it. \nStep 4: scramble your way to 12 arithmetica through whatever means possible. posse + annihilation + posse again pray to tawil + ??? <:Emoji_DFDE_M_11:1400771586545553408>  = 3 arithmetica\nStep 5: play kath X cost and win\n...\nBoss has 2nd hp bar?\nWell um <:Emoji_JL_M_03:1400771618174664775> ...\nReload?", "timestamp": "2025-08-14T18:48:26.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-14T18:49:48.546000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1405624122922373220", "filename": "TawilAgain.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 73487, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400749543288475770/1405624122922373220/TawilAgain.jpg?ex=6a3637ba&is=6a34e63a&hm=0bebf4bf32bc02d6e20e7b0a7d28d6d43a2ff160653cbc62491fbd31c9d36b12&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
